item.description:
Wrapping up our time in Vegas for Bitcoin 2026!

@iampaulgrewal, @faryarshirzad and @karacalvert joined onstage to discuss why passing federal market legislation is essential to protecting consumers and builders, and keeping our nation safe.

As always, it was great to meet up with so many of the wider Bitcoin community.

